beer.beer_description: Trooper XPA was created and developed by Iron Maiden vocalist and beer enthusiast Bruce Dickinson and the Nomad brewing team. Bruce invited Nomad to develop a local variety of Trooper with a tropical DNA for Australian taste buds and for local vans of the band. The result is a 4.5% refreshing and big flavoured XPA loaded with Australian and American hops, including 3 new varieties.
